        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "A weapon with a sisterstone striking surface can be charged with undead-destroying energy in response to violence from an undead creature. A creature wielding a sisterstone weapon gains the following activation. Only melee weapons can be made of sisterstone.",
